sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Researcher as [VLM Researcher]
  participant Python as [ego-flow Python Package]
  participant Cache as [Local Cache]
  participant Backend as [Backend]
  participant DB as [DB]
  participant Storage as [Storage]
  participant HF as [Hugging Face Datasets]

  Researcher->>Python: load_dataset("owner/repository")
  Note over Researcher,Python: 주요 인자<br/>split: None 또는 "train"<br/>streaming: boolean<br/>cache_dir: optional<br/>download_mode: reuse_cache_if_exists | force_redownload | reuse_dataset_if_exists<br/>decode: boolean<br/>with_thumbnails: boolean<br/>page_size: default 200

  Python->>Python: EgoFlowClient 준비
  Note over Python: client 인자가 있으면 재사용<br/>없으면 token, server_endpoint 또는 env로 생성

  Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/info
  Note over Python,Backend: Auth 없음<br/>dataset_manifest, video_download, python_tokens capability 확인
  Backend-->>Python: 200 server info

  alt capability missing
    Python->>Python: EgoFlowCapabilityError
  else capability ok
    alt repo_id provided
      Python->>Python: owner/repository slug만 local stub으로 분해
      Note over Python: RepositoryInfo(id=repo_id, owner_id=owner, name=repository, my_role="read")
    else repo_id omitted
      Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/repositories/resolve?slug={ownerId}/{repositoryName}
      Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token
      Backend->>Backend: requirePythonToken
      Backend->>DB: repository 조회 및 read 권한 확인
      Note over Backend,DB: owner_id + name match<br/>deactivated=false<br/>public 또는 repo_members/admin 권한
      Backend-->>Python: 200 { repository }
      Note over Backend,Python: repository fields<br/>id, owner_id, name, visibility, description, tags, my_role, created_at, updated_at
    end

    loop page while pagination.has_next
      Python->>Backend: GET /api/v1/repositories/{repoId}/manifest?page={page}&limit={pageSize}
      Note over Python,Backend: Headers<br/>Authorization: Bearer ef_raw_python_static_token

      Backend->>Backend: requirePythonToken
      Backend->>DB: repository read 권한 확인
      Backend->>DB: COMPLETED videos page 조회
      Note over Backend,DB: videos table<br/>repository_id = repoId<br/>status = COMPLETED<br/>recorded_at desc 정렬<br/>semantic_metadata scene_summary, clip_segments 포함
      Backend->>Storage: artifact metadata 및 thumbnail URL 준비
      Backend-->>Python: 200 manifest page
      Note over Backend,Python: manifest fields<br/>manifest_version<br/>repository<br/>default_artifact=vlm_video<br/>pagination.total/page/limit/has_next<br/>videos[].video_id, recorded_at, duration_sec, resolution, fps, codec<br/>videos[].scene_summary, clip_segments<br/>videos[].artifacts.vlm_video(download_url, size_bytes, sha256, content_type)<br/>videos[].artifacts.thumbnail(download_url, content_type) or null
    end

    alt streaming=true
      Python->>HF: IterableDataset.from_generator(generator)
      Note over Python,HF: generator가 manifest page를 순회하면서<br/>필요한 video artifact를 cache.ensure_video로 지연 다운로드한다.
    else streaming=false
      Python->>Cache: 모든 page manifest cache 저장
      Python->>Cache: 모든 video artifact 다운로드 또는 cache 재사용
      opt with_thumbnails=true
        Python->>Cache: thumbnail 다운로드 또는 cache 재사용
      end
      Python->>HF: Dataset.from_list(rows)
      Note over Python,HF: rows fields<br/>video_id, repository_id, repository_name, owner_id<br/>video, video_path<br/>duration_sec, fps, resolution_width, resolution_height, codec, recorded_at<br/>scene_summary, clip_segments, semantic_metadata<br/>thumbnail_path<br/>artifact_size_bytes, artifact_sha256<br/>source_type=repository
    end

    HF-->>Researcher: Dataset 또는 DatasetDict 반환
    Note over HF,Researcher: split="train"이면 Dataset<br/>split omitted이면 DatasetDict({"train": dataset})<br/>decode=true이면 datasets.Video(decode=True) cast 시도
  end

%% 참고:
%% Python package는 completed video manifest만 VLM dataset 대상으로 다룬다.
%% 진행 중인 live stream 또는 HTTP upload 상태는 manifest에 포함하지 않는다.
%% RepositoryInfo는 repository resolve response의 tags를 파싱한다.
%% manifest repository object는 현재처럼 id, name, owner_id, visibility, my_role만 사용한다.
%% Python package는 서버가 semantic_metadata object를 추가로 내려줄 경우 dataset row에 pass-through 할 수 있는 확장 지점만 둔다.
